import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import exam01 from './components/exam01'
import exam02 from './components/exam02message'
import exam03 from './components/exam03field'
import login from './components/login'
import taobao from './components/MyField_taobao2'
import exam06 from './components/exam06'
import exam07 from './components/exam07'
import exam08 from './components/exam08'
Vue.use(Router)

export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer},
    {path:'/exam01',component:exam01},
    {path:'/exam02',component:exam02},
    {path:'/exam03',component:exam03},
    {path:'/login',component:login},
    {path:'/taobao',component:taobao},
    {path:'/exam06',component:exam06},
    {path:'/exam07',component:exam07},
    {path:'/exam08',component:exam08},
  ]
})
